op_master_id: (SELECT KI.KI AS KI, RTRIM(B.BCOD) AS BCOD, B.BNAM AS BNAM, B.BNLD BNLD, B.BFLG AS BFLG FROM AEXP.A_KI AS KI JOIN DBA.BNAME AS B ON B.KESN = KI.KESN AND B.BFLG = '0') tmp

(SELECT FIRST KI.KI AS KI, V.D1FLG AS D1FLG, RTRIM(V.D1NM) AS D1NM, V.D2FLG AS D2FLG, RTRIM(V.D2NM) AS D2NM, V.D3FLG AS D3FLG, RTRIM(V.D3NM) AS D3NM, V.PJFLG AS PJFLG from AEXP.A_KI AS KI JOIN DBA.VOLUM AS V ON V.KESN = KI.KESN ORDER BY KI.KI) tmp
